name: 🎵 oh no it's palm trees again (too bad i'm losing a friend)
description:
one could start to wonder if this wannabe NFT artist isn't an impostor minting palm trees and palming mint trees, hiding his obvious incompetence behind mere technical considerations.

one could start to wonder, and at the end of the day, making people wonder is all i want (except for christmas, where all i want is you)
